7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both RankMath and Yoast SEO share a solid foundation of core features including Content Optimization, Ai Writing. Where RankMath pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Keyword Research and Rank Tracking and Serp Analysis and Reporting, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, RankMath holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Yoast SEO scores 7/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both RankMath and Yoast SEO offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. RankMath's free tier and Yoast SEO's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
